Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:03.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(358,346)}When riding a motorcycle, please wear a helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:34.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mechazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:38.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's something that\N we'd like to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:40.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:45.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We had trouble again with guys\Nfrom Bass High the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:48.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and we heard they were saying that\Nthey'd take us out for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:50.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It looks like it'll become a big fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So what are you saying you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:55.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, you have a friend at Bass High, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:58.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Would you talk to him and settle this trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:01:59.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm indebted to him already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:02.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Besides, our schools are, in fact, enemies now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:05.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So I don't think it'd work out so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:07.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I want to help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:09.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but there are things that\N I can do and things I can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:13.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But you're the only one we can depend on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:15.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've been telling you guys all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:19.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,These things happen because\N you overdo things and show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So really it's your own fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:23.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!\NYou're going too far, Mechazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:27.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Stop it, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:30.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I think Mechazawa is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:33.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We've always been totally dependent on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:37.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Guys should wipe their own asses,\Nright, Mechazawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:40.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ishida. You really\Nunderstand me very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I consider you my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:46.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But there's one thing I'd like to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:52.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In any case, you guys depend on me too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:56.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to become independent\Nif you keep acting like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You talk like you know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:00.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess, in the end, \Nwe can't even depend on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:05.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm saying this for your own good.\NIf you don't understand that, I'll leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you wanna say something,\Njust go right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:10.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Then I'll say it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:12.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Like I said, that's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:23.26,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)\bord2\be2\shad0\c&H817D8D&\fnAnna\3c&H4A3C47&\pos(189.196,65)}Coffee\N Family
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:23.26,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)\bord2\be2\shad0\fnAnna\an3\c&HAFA6D7&\3c&H4D4CE0&\pos(219.785,280)}Princess\N Peach
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:40.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\bord30\fs28\c&H4B78E7&\3c&HCAE7F0&\an7\blur0.5\fnHumana Sans Md ITC TT\frz346.586\pos(40.785,93)\clip(m 39.625 78 l 175.625 100 188.125 209 24.875 171)}Under 18\N Not Allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:38.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll go somewhere\Nto take my mind off things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:45.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\frz349.125\pos(620.835,46)\c&H31569B&\3c&H2BAAD2&\bord3\be2\fnArial\frx18\fry16}Unlimited
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:45.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\c&H4B78E7&\3c&H3E5D88&\an7\bord1.5\fscy110\blur0.5\fnHumana Sans Md ITC TT\frz346.586\move(16.994,-92,16.994,67,0,5010)}Under 18 \NNot Allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:45.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right! I got them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:54.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Crap! What am I doing in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:56.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I gave them a lecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:59.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and now I'm in this mess,\Ngetting worried if I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:02.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess that means I'm\Nactually the weakest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't care any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:07.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Since it's come to this,\NI'll fall until I hit rock bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:09.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,ls something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Seven lined up, but no pachinko balls come out, and they're stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:15.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on? Fix it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:19.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I apologize. I'll try checking it now,\Nso could you please step aside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:27.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It looks like the wiring isn't connected properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The pachinko balls aren't coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't stick your pachinko card in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:49.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Speeding on my motorcycle is\N the best thing I can do when I'm irritated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:53.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The freezing wind is piercing my skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but it feels good right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:59.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It gives me an endless high.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Customer pulling in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.61,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord20\shad0\c&HBCD4F6&\3c&H4368A9&\fnAveria Sans\fs22\b0\pos(261.703,148)\clip(m 219.75 126 l 302.5 126 302.5 149 219.75 148)}Regular
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.61,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord20\shad0\c&HBCD4F6&\3c&H537943&\fnAveria Sans\fs16\b0\pos(368.196,145)\clip(m 321.75 126 l 321.75 147 415.75 147 415.75 126)}High Octane
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.61,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord15\shad0\c&HBCD4F6&\3c&H368E9C&\fnAveria Sans\fs22\b0\pos(474.69,149)\clip(m 433.875 126 l 433.875 148 517.75 148 517.75 126)}Diesel
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Would you like us to fill it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:09.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, fill it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm filling it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:17.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it,\Nthe gas tank is here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, no kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:28.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kamiyama, I wonder if\Nthere's anything interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:32.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if Mechazawa was riding\N on a motorcycle or something and speeding,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,that'd be very interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:35.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but there's no way something like that would...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:40.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's riding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:41.52,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord3\be2\c&H5B5A4F&\3c&HC9DFD9&\fnAnna\b0\frz4.268\frx2\fry2\pos(210.722,7)}Road \NClosed
