Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's broken again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He broke into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about saying this earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but this is because he wasn't wearing a helmet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not the point, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:22.52,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\c&H5C5659&\3c&HE3E3E2&\bord4\be2\fnAnna\b0\fscy95\move(216.386,191,363.665,191,0,20520)}Dead\N End
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:06.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If something like this happens in a TV show,\Nit gets fixed before you know it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:09.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but it's really busted into so many pieces\Nthis time that we can't say such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:10.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You can't even recognize the original shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:14.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess we have to deal with it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:19.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Unless we do something right away,\Nthey'll be picked up as trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:22.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I wonder if we can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:25.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you think you can't,\Nyou won't be able to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's important for you\N to be willing to take on a challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is that how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:32.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mechazawa is an important\Nacquaintance to us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:36.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's our acquaintance,\Nalthough not quite a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:45.84,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,400)\pos(356.867,148)\c&H0FD3F5&\be1\shad3}Repair Complete
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:13.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We don't know anyone like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:26.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Relax, just come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:30.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:35.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you don't stop it now, I'll call for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:39.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. If you can, why don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,People see things\N but pretend not to see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:49.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This area is our turf,\N so everyone's too scared to defy us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:52.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No one will help you, so give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:53.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You brutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:56.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What a lively woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We'll treat you real nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:11.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:14.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you,\Nriding a weird motorcycle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:17.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who do you think we are, moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't think you can get away from this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:23.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Looks like you won't understand\Nunless you suffer a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:34.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm firing the second one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:37.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This guy's snapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He does crazy stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's run away for now!\N Damn you! We'll get even with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They're gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:53.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.\NPlease at least tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:56.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not much of anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? Looks like the police have finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:04.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But they were a little too late,\Nbecause I've solved the case.
