Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:36.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:40.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm also beginning to think \Nthat this show is doing pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:43.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I think it's okay to say it's\Na social phenomenon by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:48.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(3.399,331)}I heard that celebrities are also\Nlooking forward to this show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(137.082,465)}It's fun!
